{
  "stem": "8916.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't recall the-- that teacher.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I recall my first one, but not this one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was studying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was really advancing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was learning Gemara and--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We used to go in the-- in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And of course there weren't any public schools or anything, but you know, we talk about this business about people not resisting and not running away and all this, but there was a resistance.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We did resist.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- we-- we-- taught ourselves.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People with talent performed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We sang.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We created poems.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was entertainment.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "People went to the synagogue, which was all prohibited, of course, under-- under penalty of death.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they couldn't-- they couldn't suppress that part of the-- of the spirit.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you know, what-- what-- what they-- what they did was they would-- we would take songs of-- popular songs of the time and add different lyrics to it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, many of them were quite sad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were-- some of them were humorous, but the humor was gallows humor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, that--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I do.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I can't sing it for you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe in a-- maybe after a little while I can, but not right now.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a-- I mean, there was a song about Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Treblinka was a death camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, eventually, you know, when people found out the fact that transports were going to death camps.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was Treblinka, there, there is a place for every Jew.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] You can go in, but you cannot come out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Treblinka [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was set to a popular song at the time, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[SINGING IN YIDDISH]",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not at the time.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
